cs.IR, cs.CL, cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.DS

The paper discusses the task of large-scale answer retrieval, which involves retrieving relevant answers from a huge corpus of documents. This task is related to information retrieval (cs.IR), natural language processing (cs.CL), and machine learning (cs.AI, cs.LG). Additionally, the paper establishes baselines using both neural encoding models and classical information retrieval techniques, indicating a focus on data science (cs.DS).
